sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor L as Landlord
    participant EB as ERP backend
    participant OA as messpunkt.io<br/>OAuth 2.1 server
    participant API as messpunkt.io<br/>Partner API

    rect rgba(229,246,253,0.7)
    Note over L,OA: Phase 1 — Authentication & Consent (one-off per connect)
    L->>EB: click "Connect messpunkt.io"
    EB-->>L: redirect to /oauth/authorize<br/>response_type=code · PKCE S256<br/>scope=read:units read:devices read:readings
    L->>OA: GET /oauth/authorize
    OA-->>L: login (Entra SSO)
    OA-->>L: consent screen:<br/>scopes + Property picker<br/>(nothing pre-selected)
    L->>OA: approve + pick 2 of 50 Properties
    OA-->>EB: redirect ?code=...&state=...
    EB->>OA: POST /oauth/token<br/>code + code_verifier + DPoP key
    OA-->>EB: access_token (≤1 h, DPoP-bound)<br/>property_scope: [uuid-A, uuid-B]<br/>+ rotating refresh_token
    end

    rect rgba(232,245,233,0.7)
    Note over EB,API: Phase 2 — Authorized API calls (per request)
    EB->>API: GET /whoami<br/>Authorization: DPoP <token><br/>DPoP: <proof JWT>
    API->>API: verify DPoP proof<br/>read property_scope claim
    API-->>EB: 200 OK · property_scope=[A,B]
    EB->>API: GET /properties/{A}
    API-->>EB: 200 OK (Property A)
    EB->>API: GET /properties/{C}<br/>(C ∉ scope)
    API->>API: resource filter
    API-->>EB: 404 Not Found<br/>(existence of C not leaked)
    end

    rect rgba(255,243,224,0.7)
    Note over L,API: Phase 3 — Landlord edits scope later
    L->>OA: dashboard: remove Property B<br/>add Property D
    OA->>OA: update connection<br/>+ audit-log entry
    Note over EB,API: next token refresh (≤1 h)<br/>carries new property_scope [A, D]
    end
